messages.messageBody:
I like David Mitchell and Robert Webb. Their myspace page is filled with
some of their stuff: http://www.myspace.com/mitchellandwebb

David Mitchell is on some of the gameshows like QI and Have I got News for
You as well as a radio gameshow he hosts called Pants on Fire (I think) that
I heard the other week accidently--I think dinner prep ran late one day and
the show came on the radio.

But I like their mac ads.

Schuyler
www.waynforth.blogspot.com

messages.messageBody:
I was looking for one of my favorite British comedians a while ago and
stumbled across the pc versus mac ads. So when the mention of them came up I
figured they were running the UK ones in the US. Nope, turns out there is a
whole different series there. So, for those of you who like a British take
on things: http://www.apple.com/uk/getamac/

Schuyler
www.waynforth.blogspot.com
